data.title: Westminster School for Young Children
data.meta_description: Westminster School for Young Children in Nashville, TN - serving 1 to 5 year olds. We are NAEYC accredited and 3 Star rated. Hours are 8:45-2:00. WSYC partners with families to provide developmentally appropriate preschool education in a respectful, creative and nurturing environment.
data.text:
HOURS OF OPERATION

8:45 a.m. - 12:00 p.m. Monday

8:45 a.m. - 2:00 p.m. Tuesday through Friday

Faculty and staff participate in professional development and planning on Monday afternoons.

Summer hours at Camp Westminster are 9:00 am to 2 pm Monday through Friday.
